{"type": "article", "id": 2239, "title": "爱马仕巴塞罗那橱窗", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:37:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222300qBa6McrNg2l1IwbE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">来自法国 Zim &amp; Zou 工作室为爱马仕巴塞罗那一家店铺设计的橱窗——狐狸窝，除了那只狐狸是皮制的，其他所有装置均为纸质，纯手工制作。鲜亮的橘色是爱马仕的标志色，其中展出的爱马仕领带、丝巾、瓷器仿佛都体现着狐狸主人的品味，似乎可以让人感受到它的日常生活。好玩、耐看还带着艺术气息的橱窗，令人过目不忘。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135139MzOsEnWNDbv4q8Rg.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135141CkiKT43bFyI0Lx5J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">、<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141025mYavrpZjqeS375Ow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135152CcptgK1zLVQ7MYe6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135153X6NW1DaxwGptyfMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135154VbEjlmJDyYUC2oTA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.784375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}